728852f-a.title: Richmond: Forest Street - Jones Street
728852f-a.text:
Forest Street, west of Jones Street (vantage point),
Bull's Head. The view is southwestward across truck gardens,
toward Victory Boulevard.
April 26,1929
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
